high_descs: Turn around move towards the sofa.
Take the fork on the sofa.
Turn around move towards the dining table.
Keep the fork on the table.

high_descs: Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the sofa on your right.

Place the fork on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: To place the fork on the dining table.
